by jvasseur at 2019-06-07T14:29:17Z

AFAI class are not part of CSS but of HTML and then other specs that build on top of HTML can use them (CSS class selectors and Javascript `getElementsByClassName`).

According to this I don't think we should use CSS in the name of the function.

